      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm working on my final paper for my intro to anthro class. i need help with a section on the evolution of social structures. can you explain the main differences between how \"modern\" civilizations are structured compared to more \"primitive\" social groups? just trying to get the core concepts down for my outline.",
